title: What about duo Jungle???
body:
Hello

I'm trying to have fun doing duo jungle, but the thing is i don't know any good duos in jg. If you know any pls tell!!

replies.body: Duo Jg is pretty fun, when my friends and I do it in norms we usually roll shaco and a bruiser. Many lels.
lol, me and a friend did aatrox and lee sin, it worked, but he got all the kills ;_;
